    *   Copy of the original invoice.
    *   Copy of the PO and signed delivery receipt.
    *   Correspondence confirming the dispute.
    *   Calculation sheet showing how the adjusted payment amount was derived.
3.  **Ensure Compliance with Delegation of Authority (DOA):**
    *   Identify the appropriate level of management required to sign off on a manual payment (based on the dollar amount).
